Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:12.74,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}明明这么喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:24.21,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2\fad(50,0)}我们 分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:31.67,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}听到你这句话的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:36.40,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}脑中一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:43.19,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}身体内游走的火花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:49.80,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}忘记你的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:55.83,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}就能继续向前吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:01.95,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}不知为何 泪如雨下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:08.40,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}竭尽全力 尽心尽力 活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:14.32,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}一直是这么过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:20.44,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur2\shad0.2}不能说 不能说的再见
