Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:13.15,sign 黑体,natsu,0,0,0,,{\pos(909,251)}来自绝园魔法使的通告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:12.74,*Default,haya,0,0,0,,那个…这不会是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…指我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:19.23,*Default,haya,0,0,0,,绝园魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:22.90,*Default,haya,0,0,0,,终于就要压轴登场啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:23.82,*Default,haya,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:26.96,每集标题,samon,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,502)}心怀诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:04.83,*Default,samon,0,0,0,,幽灵不过是人疑神疑鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.19,*Default,samon,0,0,0,,不过总感觉有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:12.32,*Default,samon,0,0,0,,不…这种时候应该要装作很害怕才更可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:14.63,*Default,haya,0,0,0,,一但少女情窦初开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:16.29,*Default,samon,0,0,0,,可是谁都束手无策的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:17.81,*Default,haya,0,0,0,,一切才刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.52,*Default,samon,0,0,0,,接下来会越来越精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:22.25,*Default,samon,0,0,0,,饭呢？ 热水澡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:27.72,每集标题,hakaze,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,502)}徘徊的亡灵
